*倉庫コード大小チェック
     IF       DSP-SOKCD1  >  DSP-SOKCD2
              MOVE      8    TO   ERR-FLG
              MOVE     "R"   TO   EDIT-OPTION  OF  DSP-SOKCD1
              MOVE     "C"   TO   EDIT-CURSOR  OF  DSP-SOKCD1
              GO             TO   PARA-CHK-EXIT
     ELSE
              MOVE     "M"   TO   EDIT-OPTION  OF  DSP-SOKCD1
