*******************    DSP-BTTIME =    DEN-F47 AND
*******************    DSP-BTTORI =    DEN-F01 AND
*******************    DSP-SOKCD1 =    DEN-F48
                   IF  DSP-BTDATE =    DEN-F46 AND
